{"tid":1931913,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"排華殺到！Hongkongers is not Chinese 刻不容緩！","createTime":"2020-03-18T11:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T14:34:39.000Z","uid":89160,"like":96,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2a68bca45788f541c66bde442277f7c85ef987c1","tid":1931913,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「排華」</span></span></strong>呢樣野已經浮晒上面，疫情一退可能更加大鑊，我見好多香港人係 twitter 都仲講乜野 Mainland Chinese 唔同 Chinese 唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，講到一口泡，真係好擔心。<br />\n<br />\nRacism 呢味野好膚淺既遮，一係認皮膚顏色，一係就你就自己認。<br />\n<br />\n膚色你改唔到，你點都會受到影響，但你可以減輕佢，例如<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>點認同自己既身份其實可以改變</span></ins></strong>。<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>正如台灣人，一樣「被Chinese」左好多年，但佢地唔會好似香港人咁大中華上身，或者<span style=\"font-size: large;\">貪方便</span>認 Chinese。</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>係，好多國家都唔當 Hongkongers 唔係一個種族，但事實你堅持落去會有成果</ins></span></strong>，台灣人堅持唔認，堅持去嘈，Taiwanese 都慢慢開始有人認同。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">嚴格黎講，呢個世界係冇 Chinese 呢個種族，基本上成個東亞洲都係黃皮黑眼架啦，唔通全部都係 Chinese？</span></strong>種族本身就係冇清楚界線，就算係白人一樣係打亂種，邊有咁多純種人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以千祈唔好再講「你天生就係 Chinese / 中國人 / 華人 改變唔到」</span></strong></span>，唔好諗住「來生不做中國人」，今生你就可以唔做。<br />\n<br />\n除外自我認同，仲有就係香港人既民族自尊。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>民族自尊唔係建基於自大，而係自強自重，反之一味媚外都唔係辦法。</ins></span></strong>今次疫情我地見到日本人脆弱既一面，但日本人係世界上既聲譽總比「中國人」為好，就係因為日本人自重自強，雖然佢地呢一代都開始退化，但人地大把老本。<br />\n<br />\n我地作為香港人 Hongkongers，今次就開始為我地下一代積返d本錢，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">出門在外要誠信有禮，記得自己就係打住香港人 Hongkongers招牌，你唔單止係你自己，更係我地香港人既整體，咁你就唔會狂妄如中國人，影衰成個民族。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJUtCHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJUtCHP.png&h=e9238cb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1cca651d97ee6507b2de80d19ca76e428e96142","tid":1931913,"uid":89160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>【眾籌：美國人口普查要人！】召喚所有人 要推到美國啲姨媽姑姐都見到！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1927751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1927751</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"772f397a94406391f832e652d573c1778461cbd1","tid":1931913,"uid":89160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:53:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wethehongkongers/videos/549389139015795/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwethehongkongers%2Fvideos%2F549389139015795%2F&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=c131602e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/wethehongkongers/videos/549389139015795/</a>"},{"pid":"5a261acb9c860f0fea3cc1c0e4325faace6a3a59","tid":1931913,"uid":177326,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:54:10.000Z","msg":"心理學上黎講，你要人唔好標籤你反而會標籤得更嚴重<br />\n而加跳出黎強調自己同中國人唔同只會適得其反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國人根本唔在乎，如果想人排華就唔好覺得自己可以置身事外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n排華代價係自己俾人排埋我接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e8eb98672252cf0c7f3a3ef167cc5e1312e5bd","tid":1931913,"uid":31832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:54:19.000Z","msg":"Hongkongers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e64c340a09079067dfb498a60ad31da4f65a51","tid":1931913,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:58:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">好多人就係過唔到「天生係中國人」呢關，但真係只係心魔，而唔係事實。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"461a9ff897333c0200ac9c3d29070a324a492a1f",